divs: Sighting Detailsi was out side with twin brother and sis 20 years old sitting on the front steps..nice sunny day few white fluffy clouds thenwe saw it hudge sliver circle ufo.and we all were stunned.couldnt stop staring for 10 mins .then it vanished.we looked at each other and all said at the same time.dont tell anyone what we saw,,just couldnt belive it but the three of us saw it so clear,,trenton frankford i have seen sightings in the night,most of the time they were looking like a star really bright.but then starting moving around ,then just vanished.
Summary: suuny day white clouds clear sighting
